Package: mrf2d
Type: Package
Title: Tools for 2-dimensional Markov Random Fields
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Freguglia
Maintainer: Victor Freguglia <victorfreguglia@gmail.com>
Description: An R package for estimation and sampling of Markov Random Fields
    and Hidden Markov Random Fields using different approaches and methods
    found in the literature.
